com.polarion.alm.tracker

Interface IDocument

  • Deprecated. 
    The 2010 Live Documents are deprecated. You are probably looking for API related to current LiveDocs - see IModule.

    @Deprecated
public interface IDocument
    Represent the document storage for IPObjects. Contains method to manage contained IPObjects.
    Author:
    POLARION SOFTWARE

Although invalid documents may still contain some objects it is advised that such objects are not processed. Other information may be incorrect too. Results of adding into invalid document are not defined.

      • addObject

        ILocalId addObject(IPObject object)
        Deprecated. 
        Add object. It may get assigned a temporary local id. Such id is valid only within the scope of this document. Use IDocumentsManager.assignIds(IDocument) for assigning real local ids. Object id from given data object is ignored.

        Sets isModified(). object can't be a null

        Parameters:
        object - object to add (will be cloned)
        Returns:
        local id (may be temporary)

      • mergeObject

        void mergeObject(ILocalId localId,
                 IPObject object)
        Deprecated. 
        Merge given object into object contained in this document.

        The term merge means to take contained object and set all fields which are common to it and to source object to value from source object (various document formats may restrict these changes).

        Sets isModified() if real change occurred. localId can't be a null object can't be a null

        Parameters:
        localId - local id
        object - source object
